quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,158,"Barindiriye ikindi kintu kugira ngo bashikire Abamarayika, canke bashikirwe n’ibihano bikwiye vy’umuremyi wawe, canke hashike bimwe mubimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wawe, k’umusi hazoshika bimwe mubimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wawe, rero umuntu ntakintu nakimwe kizomufasha kukwemera kwiwe, rero uwahora atemera kuva kera canke atagize ineza mubu Isilamu bwiwe wewe vuga uti:- ni murindire natwe turarindiriye"
  6,159,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bacanishije idini ryabo nukuba imirwi n’iyindi, ntamigenderanire iri hagati yawe nabo, ntankeka urubanza rwabo ruri ku Mana hanyuma izo babwira ivyo bahora bagira"
  6,160,"Uwuzogira igikorwa ciza, azohembwa nkuko yagikoze incuro cumi, n’uwuzogira igikorwa kibi ntazorihwa atari kubingana nivyo yakoreye kandi ntibazo hemukirwa"
  6,161,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe Umuremyi wanje yarandongoye munzira igororotse y’idini ry’ukuri, kuko ariryo dini ry’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) kuko yari indongozi, kandi ntiyari mu bantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  6,162,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri amasengesho yanje, hamwe n’ibisabisho vyanje, n’ubuzima bwanje, n’urupfu rwanje, vyose biri ku Mana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  6,163,"Ntawe bicuditse nawe, nibi nivyo nategetswe n’Imana yanje, nanje ndi mubambere mubitanze kuba ndi umu Isilamu"
  6,164,"Vuga uti:- mbega mfate uwundi muremyi atari Imana mugihe ariwe muremyi w’ibintu vyose, n’umutima w’umuntu uwariwe wese ntugira ibicumuro atari kubwawo wonyene, canke uwuzo kwikorera ntazokwikorera ikintu c’uwundi muntu, hanyuma ingaruka yanyu ni ku Muremyi wanyu nayo izobabwira ivyo mwahora mutumvikana ko"
  6,165,"Nayo niyo yabagiriye ngo mufate ibibanza vy’ababayeho ng’aha kw’Isi, hanyuma yarabahaye iteka bamwe muri mwebwe kubandi kandi rininiya kugira ngo ibahe ibibazo kuri ivyo yabahaye, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe aroroshe cane muguhana mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene imbabazi nyinshi na nyene Impuhwe zihagije"